Every Time Selena Gomez Proved She Can Wear Literally Anything Pop Culture Now Staff Start Slideshow Slide of 
No one shines brighter than Selena Gomez on a red carpet, but the singer doesn't need to be under the spotlights to stun. 
The 24-year-old pop princess turns head no matter what she's wearing. Whether she's in a barely-there bathing suit or oversized overalls, Gomez has an effortless flair for fashion. 
To channel the "Same Old Love" singer's signature style, be sure to check out her Womanista Approved picks! 
Which of these looks is your favorite? (Photo: Instagram/selenagomez)
